  "title": "The Fisherman House",
  "description": "Adds a fisherman house randomly generating in the world, could contain loot !!!",
  "body": "<!-- Header / Logo -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YXUEuvP.png\" alt=\"Nightbeam Studio Mod Logo\"/>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative separator line\"/>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Social Links -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/TJc3CxR4jK\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Discord&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Join our Discord server\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@nightbeamstudio\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=YouTube&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=youtube&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Visit our YouTube channel\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=GitHub&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=github&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Sponsor us on GitHub\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/nightbeamstudio/projects\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=CurseForge&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=curseforge&logoColor=white\" alt=\"See our projects on CurseForge\"/>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/organization/nightbeam\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&message=Modrinth&color=ECEBE6&labelColor=2F4858&style=for-the-badge&logo=modrinth&logoColor=white\" alt=\"Visit our Modrinth organization page\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- About Section -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative separator line\"/>\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/about.png\" alt=\"About This Mod Header\"/>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Mod Preview -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9V52E2t.png\" alt=\"Preview of the Fisherman House in Minecraft, showing a wooden house by the ocean with a dock and fishing areas\"/>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Support Button -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/nightbeamstudio\">\n    <img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/5c14e387dab576fe667689cf/670f5a0171bfb928b21a7e00_support_me_on_kofi_beige.png\" alt=\"Support Nightbeam Studio on Ko-fi to help fund new Minecraft mods\" Width=\"400px\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Description -->\n<p>\nThe <strong>Fisherman House Mod</strong> adds unique, fully furnished fisherman houses to Minecraft. These structures spawn naturally in oceans, beaches, and nearby areas. Each house features a villager named <strong>Saylor</strong> and may contain valuable loot such as fishing rods, treasure maps, or other rare items. The mod enhances exploration, adds life to ocean and beach biomes, and provides players with new opportunities for trading and adventure.\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative separator line\"/>\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/media.png\" alt=\"Media Gallery Header\"/>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Media Gallery -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/xhdDSB9.png\" alt=\"Exterior view of the Fisherman House in Minecraft, showing the building from a distance\"/>\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PUoChBQ.png\" alt=\"Interior of the Fisherman House with furniture, storage chests, and villager interactions\"/>\n</p>\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative separator line\"/>\n</p>\n\n<!-- Features -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/sponsors/MeherBenSalem\">\n    <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/features.png\" alt=\"Features Header\"/>\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Spawns:</strong> Fisherman houses appear naturally in all <strong>Ocean biomes and Beaches</strong> across the Minecraft world.</li>\n  <li><strong>Villager:</strong> Each house contains a villager named <strong>Saylor</strong>, who behaves like a fisherman and can be interacted with for trading or quests.</li>\n  <li><strong>Loot:</strong> Houses may contain randomly generated loot, including fishing tools, treasure maps, rare materials, and unique collectibles for players to discover.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>\nTo enjoy the <strong>Fisherman House Mod</strong>, explore the oceans and beaches in your Minecraft world. Look for small wooden houses near water, which are home to the villager <strong>Saylor</strong>. You can interact with Saylor to trade fishing-related items or collect treasures from inside the house. Some houses may contain randomly generated loot, so be sure to explore multiple locations. Use boats to reach remote houses, and enjoy the added life and adventure in ocean biomes!\n</p>\n\n<!-- Installation -->\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HkPJwSd.png\" alt=\"Decorative separator line\"/>\n  <img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Fuzss/modresources/main/pages/commons/headers/installation.png\" alt=\"Installation Header\"/>\n</p>\n\n<div>\n  <p><strong>⏩ Supported Minecraft Versions:</strong> 1.16.5, 1.17.1, 1.18.2, 1.19.2, 1.19.4, 1.20.1, 1.20.4, 1.20.6, 1.21.1, 1.21.4, 1.21.5, 1.21.8</p>\n  <p><strong>⏩ Supported Platforms:</strong> NeoForge, Forge, or Fabric mod loaders</p>\n</div>",
